Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:36.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be in the middle of conducting business if you're coming at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:37.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You need a certificate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:38.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:43.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I wish you'd hurry up and become a merchant who makes others flinch at the mention of your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:45.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:50.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, is there anyone in the Trading Guild who's heading to Ramtra?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:52.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, everyone is coming in here saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:55.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fall for a shepherd lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:01.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who could safely walk in that area is that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:05.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand what the church thinks about it without me saying anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:09.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to get into trouble, don't get yourself involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:10.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:15.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That fairy, Nora, is a girl you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:21.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is there some place you want the \Ncertificate addressed to? Or unsigned?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:24.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please address it to the Remerio Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:30.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you marginally buy since you've decided on a place to sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:35.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll understand when you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:38.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a huge price fluctuation or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:40.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:44.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Since this is about you, I'm sure it'll fall in a good direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:45.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:49.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's a bit early for you to have a girl, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your earnings will simply vanish in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:55.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't invest in her if there weren't some collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:57.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:59.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:00.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wish me luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:04.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:09.40,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and Swirling Conspiracy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait, Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:15.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They were pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that I was a lovely snow flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kinds of guys are like starving dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll kidnap you if you give them attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:25.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm kidnapped, then you just need to save me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:29.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll save you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:32.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who actually saved {\i1}you{\i0}, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:38.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what kind of collateral you were expecting, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you start investing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:48.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew you liked blondes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like that slim look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Or could it be the part about her hardships?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you like shepherds?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:59.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, what the chief said was something like a greeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:02.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:07.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Nora was a bit nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:10.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I didn't have fun talking with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:14.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like I wasn't thinking of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:16.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's absolutely nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:22.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I only intended to tease you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:25.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:29.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing you say it so seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:33.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:36.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:37.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Males say anything to get what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:49.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear by the things that I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:55.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that knights express their faith by entrusting their swords and shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What about a merchant like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you my faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I will entrust you with honey-preserved peaches!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say you would buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:14.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There are things you should and shouldn't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:17.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I asked it for it cutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:19.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying you should have asked me honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell you to use your wiles to coax me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was cute though, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:28.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me more excited than
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,having my plans turn out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I really was happy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you still be mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm not mad, not mad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:48.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand being separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:53.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it'd be problematic if we got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, business can sure be scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to use your head to earn money, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,if you don't use it well and your plans fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:14.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll end up like the Ratpearon Company and have your armor sold at half its price.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we use it well, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:21.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,we can make a huge profit without using any funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best way to earn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:29.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But being in temporary debt just doesn't sit well with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean marginal buying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:32.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:35.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You bought armor at half price for 100 Rumione,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:38.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,which means that you're in debt with Ratpearon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:39.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:42.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then sell the armor for its original price at the Remerio Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:46.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The debt will be dealt between the two companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:50.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought twice the goods, so my profit will be twice as large, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:55.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it doesn't sit well with you, it'll be worth enduring, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:20.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where the monk manages?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:24.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We should hear some prayers, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:31.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably can't hear any other sounds because of the noise from eating my meat pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That was some nice sarcasm,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:38.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but to recover my honor, I can hear the sounds of people inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:39.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there are people inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:42.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but it feels dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:45.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, it's not a fun feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will happen from hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get any money if I don't sell these goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get any nourishment if I don't eat this meat pie, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}my {\i0}nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What? If you wanted some, you should have told me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:00.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:10.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're supposed to be open until the Sabbath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some special reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah... kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just arrive in this city today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:20.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I arrived a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like a lot happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:26.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I will help you if you have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:29.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:30.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:33.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We await your next arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:37.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence Craft!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:45.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought some armor from Ratpearson, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:49.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, there was a messenger from Polson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:53.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ratpearson Company sent a credit claim to this company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:54.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Credit claim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:02.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your companion's business has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:10.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There has been a decline in armor for a while, and it's worth nothing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratpearon used their inferior stock to put him into debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:16.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and the rights to it have been transferred to this company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:20.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning, your companion has a huge debt to settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, he's bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They've tricked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:36.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We both entered this contract knowing the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:37.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Mr. Remerio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:41.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a merchant too, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:47.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You bought 100 Rumione worth of armor from the Ratpearson Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:53.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your debt amounts to 47 and 3/4 Rumione with a deadline on loans, with no collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:56.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move on to your repayment of the debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:10:01.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't pay, we will have to demand the Rowen Trading Guild to shoulder your debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:02.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:06.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your loans will be due the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We will wait for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:13.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, please gather 47 and 3/4 Rumione and pay us back every coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:17.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I will sell the armor at a high price, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:20.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We will perform the liquidation in two days. Is that acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:21.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:23.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:27.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me say this just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:33.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens, our street stalls will be up near the city exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:36.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come by anytime if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:40.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your words, but I'm sure I won't be needing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:43.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be busy with all your business negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to seeing you in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,May God protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:01.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:05.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:08.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, the goods behind us are now garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:12.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I didn't hear it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be bankrupt at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:25.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Information between merchants is just like being looked upon by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:29.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be found no matter where we go and do business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:32.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, I can no longer return to being a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:37.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, those who suffer wounds in a fight are suddenly eaten down to the last bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:38.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:44.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to return the 47 Rumione, and it'll be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:46.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible for me to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Horo the Wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:53.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll be of help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:57.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, paying back the food expense will surely help me-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'd earn what I ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:04.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:08.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes, I'll put my honor on the line and run away with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have to use the power of this wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:15.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised that you'd take me to the northern forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have us stumbling here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:21.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I swear I'll keep my promise. Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:28.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I might ask for your help when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:30.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:35.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's head for the Trading Guild for now. You wait at the inn-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My partner is in a crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:42.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,do I look like an immoral wolf who can groom her fur at leisure at the inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:51.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:55.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trading Guild is our home town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a special meaning when we take women there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine if you explain our situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we going to explain it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:07.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a disaster if the church persecutes us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:11.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should just say that we're in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:21.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lot smarter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you'll be with me as a business partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:29.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:32.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Their welcomes are pretty tough, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:40.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me first ask, just who is this beautiful lady and where did she come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:43.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my business partner who trades with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Business?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:51.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Milone Company in Pattsio, she sold fur that was assessed at 140 Thoreni silver coins,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and raised it to 210 coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:59.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't invest in things without any collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:03.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are guys like you, sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:10.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written in the scriptures to not open any unknown boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:11.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:27.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}Someone from the Remerio Company came by earlier requesting us to shoulder a debt, so I know the outline.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, you were greedy and failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:32.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that makes things simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:39.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The debt would probably be shouldered by the guild, but
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:42.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you just need to pay it back on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:46.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You were swindled, extorted, diseased and injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:52.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}If the debt were to be pushed onto us, it'll be different this time instead of us risking our honor to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can save you is God, or this beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:01.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate, but I can't grant you a single bit of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:06.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, being firm and taking this attitude will be reason for me being in that lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:08.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the law for the entire guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:14.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if someone else were to be treated special, I would be angry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:17.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, you cannot borrow from others within the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:21.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline for the debt is in two days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:24.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Remerio also invested in armor and failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:27.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm sure they will come to collect your debt without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, your failure will be known the day after tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:33.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and I will have to restrain you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:36.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What conclusion have you come to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:42.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I cannot gather 47 Rumione within two days, then there will be no tomorrow for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:44.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:47.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow will come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:52.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But it will be a dark, tough, and burdening tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:59.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}If you rowed a long-distance trade ship for ten years, I'm sure you'd be able to pay off the 47 Rumione.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:03.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You can dig holes and mine too, but that's only if you're lucky and survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:06.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an empty dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:11.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:16.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sins must be punished. I just have to do the natural thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:17.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:23.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do the best that you can in these two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need help doing business, I'll help as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:31.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as much as you can so that you can walk free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:34.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:38.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll earn it in two days, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are loopholes in business that you may not know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are paths you can see only when you're cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:54.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else you want to ask or say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:55.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:57.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:03.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:08.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please think of something surprising to say when I pay back my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be fine if you can say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:17.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,47 Rumione in two days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:37.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:39.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'll fight debt with debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anybody in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I trade without aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:48.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anyone who would let me borrow a lot of money, but
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:51.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a lot of people who would help me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:54.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll be fine if there are 47 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:56.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:18:00.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lawrence, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring some profitable story?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:03.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I still know a lot of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:20.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry, but we're busy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:23.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost the end of the year and the price of wheat and meat are rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:28.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:31.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have the next place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:33.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:38.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stock up for spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:07.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:10.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I make that deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:12.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:50.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:54.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't walk properly in this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:03.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:12.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for coming since the market is closed, but I have an earnest request.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you've been asking at many places.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:17.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of the decline in armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:22.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I failed because of my naive outlook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:25.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Naive outlook? I guess there's also that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:30.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, no one else but God can predict the decline of goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It is unjust to blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:37.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You have brought me profit before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:41.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would help you if you were to ever be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:41.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:48.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I cannot see in your attitude a willingness to follow God's teachings and show sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:51.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:59.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You try to get others to sympathize and lend you money, but you walk around with a woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:01.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make light of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:15.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just wander into the middle of the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:21.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:22.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the inn-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't met yo-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:43.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:19.97,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven apples on the witch's tree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:25.35,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:30.53,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,In spring time I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:33.27,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then skipping along,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:35.83,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:41.26,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:46.59,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:51.93,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I danced with the peanuts for the flies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:54.56,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Till someone had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:57.62,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,To say hello for every good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:02.58,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw some sugar stars
